Package project

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Options
    Options is the class where all methods regarding the options available for the hotel are written and it also contains the methods for importing and exporting data to the different csv files
    Reservation
    Reservation is the class where the each reservation is made, it consists of various get and set methods which are used to instantiate and grab values and variables the reservation objects
    ReservationMenu
    ReservationMenu is the class the runs the menu for the l4Hotels System.
    Room
    Room is the class that sets up the Room Objects, these objects consist of a roomType, whether or not the resident wants breakfast and the occupancy with regards to children and adults
    RoomInfo
    RoomInfo contains and changes with regards to availability the data stored on the l4Hotels csv file.
    Test
    Test runs the entire System, containing the main method
